Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在让我们快速了解 HTML 到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我们可以用它做什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上 HTML 代表超文本标记语言和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我们之前是如何了解到 HTML 是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心网络技术以及 CSS 和 JavaScript。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HTML 是一种标记语言，我们的 Web 开发人员可以使用它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结构和描述任何网页的全部内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请注意我所说的标记语言，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 HTML 真的不是一种编程语言。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是一种标记语言，因为我们使用它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形容某事。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 HTML 的情况下，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确实使用元素来描述内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:01:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们有不同的元素可以用来描述
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同类型的内容。例如，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有我们在讲座中已经使用过的 P 元素
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那里创建了我们的第一个网页。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们在那里使用 P 元素来创建一个段落，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们真的有各种不同的元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以创建链接的元素，创建页面标题，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图片、视频等等，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如您将在本节中学习的那样。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上贯穿整个课程，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后，正如我们在那堂课中学到的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那里建立了我们的第一个网页，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络浏览器，例如谷歌浏览器，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上理解 HTML 代码并可以渲染它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为最终网站，所以我们可以看到的网站
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在浏览器中。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这本质上就是 HTML 和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以用它做什么。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在让我们稍微放大一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HTML 元素的剖析。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上看一下构建块
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个 HTML 元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次，我们在这里查看段落元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所看到的那样。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的所有这些实际上都是元素本身。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一个 HTML 元素通常由三部分组成。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是开始标签，它是元素的名称。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这种情况下，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是包裹在小于中的P而不是在更大的巢穴中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符号，可能它们还有其他名称，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是我喜欢称呼这些符号的方式。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它小于 P 然后大于。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后，在那之后，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们基本上有了元素的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这个例子中，这只是文本，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能还有其他类型的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如，一个元素本身可以包含，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个元素，我们称之为子元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些元素，比如图像，实际上已经
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有内容，只有开放技术。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这一切当然会变成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们开始编写 HTML 时非常直观。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我谈到开始标签时，你知道我在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或结束标签或内容，并谈到结束标签，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它与开始标签基本相同，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一个斜线。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它只是用 P 打开它的段落元素
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们用斜线 P 关闭它，好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对于没有的元素内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如我之前提到的图像元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们实际上省略了结束标签。 所以在那种情况下，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只有开始标签，仅此而已，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然会看到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我们开始将图像集成到网页中。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，那是真的，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始学习 HTML 和练习所需的一切，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我们在下一节课中要做的。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's now very quickly learn what HTML actually is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and what we can do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically HTML stands for Hypertext Markup language and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,remembered how we learned earlier that HTML is one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,core web technologies along with CSS and JavaScript.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HTML is a markup language that we web developers can use to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,structure and describe the entire content of any webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So notice how I said markup language,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because HTML is really not a programming language.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a markup language because we use it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to describe something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in the case of HTML,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we do describe content using elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:01:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we have different elements that we can use to describe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,different types of content. So for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have the P element that we already used in the lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where we created our very first webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so we use the P element there to create a paragraph,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we really have all kinds of different elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So elements to create links, to create page headings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,images, video, and a lot more,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as you will learn throughout this section.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And basically throughout the entire course,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then, as we also learned in that lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where we built our very first webpage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,web browsers, such as Google Chrome,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do essentially understand HTML code and can render it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as a final website, so website that we can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the browser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is essentially what HTML is and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what we can do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now let's just zoom in a little bit and take a look at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the anatomy of a HTML element.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically take a look at the building blocks of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,each HTML element.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And again, we are looking at the paragraph element here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as you can see by the P.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so all of this here is actually the element itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now an HTML element is usually made up of three parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First is the opening tag, which is the name of the element.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So in this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's the P wrapped in the less than in the greater den
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,symbols, probably they have some other names,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that's how I like to call the symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it's less than P and then greater than.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have basically the content of the element.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So in this example, that is just text,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but there might be other types of content.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, an element can contain in itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,another element which we then call a child element.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also some elements such as images have actually
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no content at all and have only an opening tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And all of this will of course become
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,very intuitive as we start writing HTML.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just so that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you know what I'm talking about when I speak of opening tag
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or closing tag or content, and speaking of the closing tag,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it is basically the same as the opening tag,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but with a slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it opens its paragraph element simply with the P
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we then close it with slash P, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now for elements that do not have content
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,such as the image element that I mentioned before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we actually omit the closing tag. So in that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we only have the opening tag and that's it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we will see that in action of course
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,once we start integrating images into a webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, and that's really,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all you need in order to start learning HTML and practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is exactly what we will do in the next lecture.